These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, trance, reggae, d&b
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, bus, ship
1. the person driving the airplane is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
5. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the ship is between the fan of d&b and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | writing      | hiking | reading | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | folk  | trance   | d&b    |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus    | ship    | boat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, sudoku, video-games
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, mexican, polish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, bongani, dunhill, bolivar
1. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the mexican##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the japanese##1
7. the american is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
8. the polish is between the japanese and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Nationality   | mexican     | american | polish  | japanese |
| Cigar     | bolivar        | dunhill  | bongani    | ritmeester |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, april, october
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, canadian, german
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. the german is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in october##2
2. the argentine is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
6. the canadian is between the person who's birthday is in january and the american##2
7. the german is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday          | march | january   | october     | april     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | german | canadian   | american  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, punk, salsa, soul
House: ranch-style, palace, futuristic, colonial
1. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the palace house##1
3. the colonial house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
4. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the fan of soul is the ranch-style house##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the fan of pop##1
7. the fan of salsa is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | soul      | pop        | punk     |
| House         | futuristic | ranch-style | colonial | palace   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, colombian, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, swimming, volleyball
4 different pets are kept: cat, pony, dog, bird
1. the japanese is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the colombian is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the cat is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the far right##1
8. the colombian is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
9. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | american   | japanese   | colombian | canadian |
| Sport         | rugby      | volleyball | golf      | swimming |
| Pet     | pony | cat        | bird       | dog  |

