.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, water
House: futuristic, victorian, tower, cape-cod
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, skiing, weightlifting
1. the futuristic house is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
3. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the futuristic house##1
7. the futuristic house is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the victorian house is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
9. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta         | coffee  | iced-tea     | water         |
| House        | cape-cod | victorian | futuristic | tower         |
| Sport      | rugby         | skiing  | ice-hockey   | weightlifting |

