.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, september, january, june
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, nigerian, turkish
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, lizard, mouse
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 2. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 4. the nigerian is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in december##2
 5. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
 6. the owner of the mouse is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the turkish is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
 9. the malaysian is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in january##2
10. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | december  | january    | september | june    |
| Nationality   | canadian | nigerian | malaysian  | turkish |
| Pet           | lizard   | mouse    | dog        | horse   |

