.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, soy-milk
House: wooden, ranch-style, gothic-revival, tower
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, italian, russian
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
2. the ranch-style house is on the left of the wooden house##1
3. the russian is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
4. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the wooden house##1
6. the russian is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
7. the indonesian is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | 7up                | soy-milk  | almond-milk | juice   |
| House           | tower | ranch-style | wooden   | gothic-revival |
| Nationality   | indonesian         | dutch     | russian     | italian |

