.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, cherry, lime, peach
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, musical, romance, western
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, blood-red, apricot, ivory
1. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
4. the person eating lime is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person who likes mauve is between the person watching western movies and the person who likes ivory##2
6. the person watching romance movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | lime    | cherry  | peach  | avocado |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical | action | romance |
| Color   | apricot    | mauve     | ivory    | blood-red |

