.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, electronic, reggae
4 different pets are kept: goat, horse, pony, turtle
1. the owner of the horse is between the person drinking fanta and the fan of blues##2
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
7. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
8. the fan of electronic is the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the fan of reggae is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the goat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | coffee  | sprite    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | dubstep | reggae | blues |
| Pet           | turtle      | pony       | horse   | goat      |

