.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, reading, skydiving
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, lawyer, project-manager, teacher
City: berlin, hannover, liverpool, marseilles
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an odd position##4
2. the project-manager is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the journalist is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is the lawyer##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
6. the journalist is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the project-manager##1
8. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |        4        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | reading   | cooking    | magic-tricks    |
| Job           | teacher   | lawyer    | journalist | project-manager |
| City   | hannover    | berlin | liverpool    | marseilles         |

