4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
5. the oliveros-smoker is the canadian##1
6. the fan of indie is on the right of the french##1
7. the french is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
8. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Cigar   | chaman | fonseca | oliveros | dannemann   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b    | jazz   | indie     | blues    |
| Nationality   | dutch  | french | canadian  | nigerian |

